About Wrist

Wrist is a bi-weekly illustrative exercise to explore typography, colors, clock mechanics, and everything else that goes into watch design. Starting with one of my watches, I will be illustrating existing watches as well as exploring new watch designs.

I’m a designer and developer living in South Bay with my wonderful wife, Natalie, and working in Los Gatos at Netflix.

Prints

Like the illustrations on Wrist? Help support Wrist and add some class to your office. Check out the prints for all the watches on our store.
